title: Thought Janna looked a little dated

embed.description: I felt like the Janna skin was a little dated. Was also studying sakimichan so I pulled some aspects from her style. Enjoy Janna

body: Had so much fun doing ahri i thought i would do another one. Critiques appreciated. Enjoy!

replies.body: She's lovely! My only feedback would be to pop out her tiara a bit more, so it isn't blending in with her hair. :)
Thanks, you did her a favour!
